    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The spark of the divine in you grants the ability to overcome fatigue and grievous injuries. You do not suffer &amp;Reference[Exhaustion apply=false] from dropping to 0 Hit Points, and whenever you decrease your Exhaustion level, decrease it by an additional 1.</p><p>You gain the ability to overcome grievous injuries. As a Bonus Action when you have fewer than half of your Hit Points remaining, you can regain a number of Hit Points equal to half your Hit Point maximum.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a Long Rest.</p>",
